            "title": "5 月M2餘額按年升8.6%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">人民銀行公布，5月末，廣義貨幣(M2)餘額353.67萬億元（人民幣．下同），按年增長8.6%，增速與4月末持平，並優於預期的8.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">狹義貨幣(M1)餘額114.89萬億元，按年增長5.5%，增速較4月末擴大0.5個百分點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">流通中貨幣(M0)餘額14.69萬億元，按年增長11.9%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">前五個月淨投放現金5907億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16155136-5-%e6%9c%88m2%e9%a4%98%e9%a1%8d%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%878-6",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250507_FI_source-ap_PBC-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-06-12 17:23:40",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
