            "title": "MiniMax今挫逾9%   自3月高位大挫七成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">MiniMax(00100)今日最多挫41.2元或9.47%，低見393.8元，現跌9.29%，報394.6元，成交6.51億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250915_cr_minimax_fb.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250915_cr_minimax_fb.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">今早曾跟隨大市反彈，高見449.4元，升14.4元或3.31%，惟走勢很快逆轉，該股已連跌第7日。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">MiniMax股價踏入6月份持續向下，該股5月底收市840元，至今股價累跌53.1%。52周最高位為3月中報1330元，以此水平計算股價高位累跌70.4%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16154439-minimax%e4%bb%8a%e6%8c%ab%e9%80%be9-%e8%87%aa3%e6%9c%88%e9%ab%98%e4%bd%8d%e5%a4%a7%e6%8c%ab%e4%b8%83%e6%88%90",
